{"tid":903421,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳奕迅談生命嘅歌都被低估","createTime":"2018-11-15T14:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T16:04:44.000Z","uid":49781,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"220c991b24b8db61a90990a325d13993c8f0b888","tid":903421,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:00:32.000Z","msg":"由 活著多好<br />\n到 最後派對<br />\n再去到 完<br />\n明明咁好聽又有意義都hit唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e8dc18fed2858150c032877f7b769585a4cb8d","tid":903421,"uid":75543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"我的快樂時代  <br />\n陀飛輪<br />\n<br />\n經典之作"},{"pid":"dca77f5a2f356094c0accf1c4f0ad901fc9de9bf","tid":903421,"uid":49781,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"活著多好:<br />\n仍然在呼吸都應該　要慶賀<br />\n如果想哭　可試試對嘉賓滿座<br />\n說個笑話　紀念我<br />\n<br />\n最後派對:<br />\n活得精彩結尾切勿流眼淚<br />\n來讓我詩歌班裡悄然沉睡這是自然程序<br />\n開心的派對 散後無法聚 放我於心裡<br />\n新的工作裡 一追再去追<br />\n未開出最後的花蕊 你別要氣餒<br />\n何妨留戀一歲 多一歲 一歲<br />\n<br />\n完:<br />\n手一僵 眼閉著 未能延著 別求延著 <br />\n學會花圈棺蓋了後 就獻上 <br />\n但願步過瞻仰 你亦明白 看穿真相 <br />\n尚有些仗 全力亦打不上 <br />\n<br />\nEason唱呢類歌真係好催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a408f0ae01a45a786834d2d04976c4fd7f5fb332","tid":903421,"uid":90282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"怕死 都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afc0d3b980b31d84138524186fda23354b29b6d","tid":903421,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a408f0ae01a45a786834d2d04976c4fd7f5fb332","tid":903421,"uid":90282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"怕死 都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但氛圍上我講個三首比較沉寂"},{"pid